    "Only ACER with Bin history can consistently reach an average episodic reward above 0.7.",
    "With the help of the diversity filter, this leads to the highest number of active molecules and scaffolds.",
    "Hence, the slower convergence rate can possibly be explained by a more elaborate exploration phase.",
    "However, ACER shows a large variability.",
    "Even though SAC does generally achieve lower average episodic rewards, it is more stable and shows a larger median of active molecules and scaffolds compared to ACER utilizing Top history and Top-bottom history."
